{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Divider"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"value","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Equatable","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SQ"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transform","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"value","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A value to monitor for changes.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"transform","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The transformation to apply to transactions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within this view."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all transactions used within the view whenever "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":" changes."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Consider three identical views controlled by a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"button that changes all three simultaneously:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The first view animates rotating the “Rotation” "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view by 360"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"degrees."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The second uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to change the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“Rotation\\nModified” "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" view animation by a factor of 2."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to disable animations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced” "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text"},{"type":"text","text":" view."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code implements these animations:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction(value: flag) { t in","                        t.animation =","                            t.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction(value: flag) { t in","                        t.disableAnimations = true","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Divider\/transaction(value:_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/divider\/transaction(value:_:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Applies the given transaction mutation function to all animations used"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within the view."}],"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"fileName":"TransactionModifier.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob